-Entering Text
    Whenever text is placed within [brackets] -> a forth wall break is implied
    Typically, the text within brackets will indicate what the game understands as input for that prompt.

-If you are stuck on a task and want to exit before it is completed, you must restart the game.

-Similar to life, there are random events that happen occasionally when traveling.

-Platinum Disks [PD]:
    This is the currency native to the realm






